#: ../../developer/debugging/test-bench.rst:3 34a58cd325d14897aec3a4921e4813d5
msgid "How to set up a test bench"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/debugging/test-bench.rst:6 f2de2fcc9e6d42149071a277077e2858
msgid ""
"This guide shows how to set up simple test bench that automatically test "
"your code you’re about to push. It is written especially for ``core3`` "
"branch of ``core-admin.git`` repo, but some ideas are universal."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/debugging/test-bench.rst:8 ef682a30f8d84989b51b75ec929fd40b
msgid ""
"We will set up a spare machine (bare metal, not a virtual) that will be "
"hosting our experimental Dom0. We will communicate with it via Ethernet "
"and SSH. This tutorial assumes you are familiar with :doc:`QubesBuilder "
"</developer/building/qubes-builder>` and you have it set up and running "
"flawlessly."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/debugging/test-bench.rst:10 18d0d68815cf4a08866ea04aa1ddb8a9
msgid ""
"**Notice:** This setup intentionally weakens some security properties in "
"the testing system. So make sure you understand the risks and use "
"exclusively for testing."
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/debugging/test-bench.rst:13 2075920273784f84847cc3b60be954db
msgid "Setting up the Machine"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/debugging/test-bench.rst:17 23c0cae00f3d4553baeac01fb1a33a7b
msgid "Install ISO"
msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/debugging/test-bench.rst:20 b2b9420d64a342c792ffe56069990fc4
msgid ""
