"only network card was assigned to dom0, then *instead* of the usual "
"``sudo qubes-dom0-update <PACKAGE>`` now you run ``sudo dnf "
"--setopt=reposdir=/etc/yum.repos.d install <PACKAGE>``."
msgstr ""

